{"tid":545181,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Linux 之父 Linus Torvalds 粗口連篇，屌柒批 Intel Meltdown、Spectre 修補方法係垃圾！","createTime":"2018-01-30T09:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T02:50:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69518df59471d58c00c847bb3800ab73246c472f","tid":545181,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">以直言或說出言不遜聞名的 Linux 作業系統創辦人 Linus Torvalds，這次槓上 Intel，批評他們針對 Linux 內核的 Meltdown 和 Spectre 修補程式是垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/05145339/linus-torvalds-lc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F05145339%2Flinus-torvalds-lc3.jpg&h=235053cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/01/23/linux-creators-linus-torvalds-criticize-intel-meltdown-and-spectre-patches-are-garbages/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2Flinux-creators-linus-torvalds-criticize-intel-meltdown-and-spectre-patches-are-garbages%2F&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f58ef649\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/01/23/linux-creators-linus-torvalds-criticize-intel-meltdown-and-spectre-patches-are-garbages/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xcnnews.com/kj/3070053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xcnnews.com%2Fkj%2F3070053.html&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=07b38013\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xcnnews.com/kj/3070053.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"0889560da6bdf715f8ebfabfcd0c199d0ab0388c","tid":545181,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"Intel雖然一再表示，正竭盡全力與整個行業合作，修復熔斷/幽靈這兩個CPU漏洞，並即時公布進展，連效能損失數據也逐一公布出來。<br />\n<br />\n但是在Linux之父Linus Torvalds看來，Intel的表現實在是糟糕之極，完全搞不懂在幹什麼，而在近日與英國亞馬遜工程師David Woodhouse的一封郵件中，他更是按捺不住激動的情緒對Intel破口大罵，甚至髒話連篇。<br />\n<br />\n他一開波就說：「這一些純粹都是垃圾。Intel到底還想不想把事情搞好？有沒有人能找他們說說，告訴他們都TMD瘋了！擺脫了，如果有Intel工程師看到，和你們的主觀談談吧。」<br />\n<br />\n「BULLSHIT」(扯淡)、「COMPLETE AND UTTER GARBAGE」(徹徹底底的垃圾)、「WHAT THE F*CK IS GOING ON?」(TDM到底怎麼回事)&hellip;&hellip;Linus就用這些全部大寫的髒話發泄著自己的不滿。<br />\n<br />\nLinus之所以如此暴怒，主要是他平常的Linux內核開發工作本來就很忙，結果又被Intel捅了個大簍子，不得不花費大量時間和精力，和社區一同修復解決。<br />\n<br />\n但問題是，Intel修復的速度太慢，而且補patch質素不敢恭維，引發了效能下降、系統重啟等各種問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Intel甚至將PATCH更新設置為可選項，也就是說完全可以人為禁用，這對於需要在數據中心、雲計算等苛刻環境運行的Linux系統來說，是不可接受的。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Woodhouse對此也是相當不滿。"},{"pid":"976320ff757644ff0c89154f3b0b22f2ce358537","tid":545181,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"無競爭，市佔率太高"},{"pid":"3b77c49724484ea18ab5829c50f6717361ef9fcd","tid":545181,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"搞到linux4.15到依家都未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc61c8384f649d753bb5cad13aebc075c6a6fbe","tid":545181,"uid":33883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"啲股票都放得七七八八, (Intel高層)話之你丫! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfa4638527493c4b14cc488948ed8d3e2624559","tid":545181,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/201457_4c4104e51dde7547e177f197fddbd58a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F201457_4c4104e51dde7547e177f197fddbd58a.png&h=c0935a0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"086a81be4eb6c4aab1594813d13f183ef3a89499","tid":545181,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":